{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","title":"subtitle","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)subtitle","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"}]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"copy","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This string is displayed in the callout for the associated annotation."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/subtitle":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle","title":"subtitle","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol"}}}